        <ontology:hasDescription>The reference mountain chain of this VC is Slovak Carpathians. The reference mountain landscape of this VC is Zliechov. VC is relevant in all NUTS3 mountain regions (row57). Zliechov LAU2 village is located within the Strážov Mountains Protected Landscape Area and near to Strážov Mountain (1,213 m). The surface of the area is formed by highlands and is strongly undulating.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


