        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/phenomenal_place/48.94259439711003_18.431998357299868"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/1"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>1) Pandemic situation causes problems to game supplies. Retail chains require relatively large quantities of the same type of meat in a short time. As the game can only be hunted to a limited extent for pandemic measures, it isn&amp;apos;t easy to ensure a sufficient amount of game and logistics to retail chains. 2) The government&amp;apos;s implemented project is only temporal, and a long-term strategy to increase the amount of game meat available for domestic consumption is necessary. Overall the type of challenge faced by this VC is Current and Predicted. This VC is classified as Traditional and Innovative.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


